newsitem.title: USA: FCOJ weekly movement drops to 4.833 mln gallons.
newsitem.headline: FCOJ weekly movement drops to 4.833 mln gallons.

text.p: Florida Citrus Processors Association said frozen concentrated orange juice movement into trade channels for the week ended May 31 was 4,833,513 gallons compared with 6,146,663 gallons last week.
Imports were 334,582 gallons compared with 768,758 gallons the previous week. There were 125,805 domestic receipts for this week compared with 27,147 the previous week.
Retail movement was 829,602 gallons, while bulk movement was 3,545,307 gallons.
Current season cumulative movement was 137,646,647 gallons.
The final total pack for the season is 232,950,075 gallons.
